<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Link your hardware to your cash register system. The receipt printer automatically prints a test receipt after the TSE has been linked.<br>
Open the plentymarkets app and click on <strong>Settings</strong> in the menu. Enter the IP address of the TSE unit that is printed on the test receipt. Tap <strong>Link TSE unit</strong>.<br>
