<div class="paragraph">
<p>Proceed as described below to download TSE export files.</p>
</div>
<h5 id="_assigning_rights_for_back_end_users_3" class="discrete">Assigning rights for back end users</h5>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>People with <strong>Back end</strong> access rights can <a href="/en/business-decisions/user-accounts-access#105">only see certain areas and menus</a> in plentymarkets. This means they only have limited access to the system. If you want <strong>back end</strong> type users to download TSE exports, you have to grant them the following rights:</p>
