<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">4.</p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Register the signature card and POS at FinanzOnline</p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div class="content"><div class="paragraph">
<p>After creating the start receipt, register the signature card and POS at FinanzOnline. You need the following information to complete the registration process:<br></p>
